WEBVTT

01:19.400 --> 01:23.400
"Journey With You"

01:24.700 --> 01:26.700
(Episode 8)

01:40.700 --> 01:42.168
Time passes so quickly.

01:42.836 --> 01:44.971
The day when the Emperor
asks you to return to Talhan

01:45.205 --> 01:46.606
is less than a month away.

01:47.540 --> 01:51.120
The Emperor has dealt with the remnants of the
Imperial Uncle's faction with lightning speed.

01:51.144 --> 01:52.922
There have been many
affairs in the court recently.

01:52.946 --> 01:54.180
As a prince,

01:54.647 --> 01:55.927
you've been working hard lately.

01:56.850 --> 01:58.151
The court ministers

01:58.485 --> 02:00.405
will also become more
and more convinced of you.

02:01.087 --> 02:02.088
I know.

02:03.022 --> 02:03.890
Before, in order to

02:03.891 --> 02:04.891
deal with Yinzhou,

02:04.958 --> 02:06.292
I used every means possible.

02:07.260 --> 02:08.761
Now that Yinzhou is gone,

02:09.429 --> 02:12.065
I find doing these political
affairs utterly uninteresting.

02:14.667 --> 02:15.707
I understand how you feel.

02:16.703 --> 02:18.303
If you don't want to inherit the throne,

02:18.671 --> 02:20.871
then give more support to
your seventh younger brother.

02:21.107 --> 02:23.427
You also think the seventh
younger brother is good, right?

02:23.476 --> 02:25.156
We really have great chemistry between us.

02:32.085 --> 02:33.352
I've noticed that you

02:33.353 --> 02:34.753
haven't been looking well recently.

02:35.088 --> 02:36.088
Is it because

02:36.222 --> 02:38.662
I made you help with the
political affairs and you got tired?

02:39.826 --> 02:40.627
Speaking of which,

02:40.827 --> 02:41.860
Recently, Duan Yong and Duan Yi

02:41.861 --> 02:43.196
have also been extremely busy.

02:43.696 --> 02:45.231
Take a good rest next.

02:45.565 --> 02:47.267
I can handle the rest of the things alone.

02:50.036 --> 02:52.036
It's just that I want to
be with you all the time.

02:54.240 --> 02:55.808
Before I leave the capital,

02:56.309 --> 02:58.687
I need to take care of some things
at the Piaoxiang Pavilion.

02:58.711 --> 02:59.812
This time when I leave,

03:02.715 --> 03:04.551
I don't know when I'll
be able to come back.

03:11.224 --> 03:12.224
By the way,

03:12.792 --> 03:13.792
The other day,

03:14.527 --> 03:16.428
I had a painter draw
portraits of the two of us.

03:16.429 --> 03:18.598
We'll each have one then.

03:20.667 --> 03:21.667
In consideration of

03:22.769 --> 03:25.004
how hard you've been working,

03:26.706 --> 03:28.408
I'll give you another gift.

03:37.103 --> 03:39.096
(Pei Yanzhi)

03:41.087 --> 03:42.087
This...

03:44.324 --> 03:45.390
When you return to the grasslands,

03:45.391 --> 03:46.793
everyone will call you Feng Sui.

03:47.260 --> 03:48.540
No one will call you Pei Yanzhi.

03:49.195 --> 03:50.597
I'm afraid that after a long time,

03:50.630 --> 03:51.630
you'll forget.

03:55.501 --> 03:57.703
You should keep it close to you

03:57.704 --> 03:58.871
and think of me every day.

04:04.243 --> 04:05.243
Yanzhi,

04:05.645 --> 04:07.447
this name has a meaning.

04:08.381 --> 04:09.525
Grinding ink is silent, [Yan means
a kind of tool for grinding ink]

04:09.549 --> 04:11.751
yet it can write about
everything throughout the ages.

04:15.388 --> 04:16.689
The name you gave me,

04:18.257 --> 04:19.692
how could I dare to forget it?

04:28.067 --> 04:29.269
Although I know

04:29.969 --> 04:32.009
that you will definitely
come back after you leave,

04:32.071 --> 04:34.874
but the thought that once you leave,

04:35.008 --> 04:36.342
it might take several years,

04:36.709 --> 04:38.645
it makes my heart feel empty.

04:41.547 --> 04:42.547
A Qi,

04:43.283 --> 04:44.484
Before I leave,

04:44.717 --> 04:45.785
wherever you want to go,

04:45.885 --> 04:47.053
I'll go with you.

04:47.286 --> 04:49.822
Take it as my gift to you.

04:52.025 --> 04:53.025
Really?

05:00.867 --> 05:01.867
Look at this.

05:07.273 --> 05:07.940
Let's take this one.

05:07.941 --> 05:09.208
This is a good item.

05:09.609 --> 05:11.044
You have a good eye, miss.

05:11.678 --> 05:12.678
It smells so good.

05:16.496 --> 05:17.496
Yanzhi, come quickly.

05:17.550 --> 05:18.550
Come.

05:20.386 --> 05:21.386
Look.

05:21.554 --> 05:22.554
Look at this.

05:24.190 --> 05:24.757
Duan Yi and Duan Yong,

05:24.957 --> 05:26.669
you two go back to the
Piaoxiang Pavilion and wait first.

05:26.693 --> 05:28.961
It's inconvenient to carry so many things.

05:29.362 --> 05:30.362
Yes.

05:30.663 --> 05:32.532
Please take your time. Come again.

05:32.965 --> 05:33.766
Those things

05:33.800 --> 05:35.234
are all specialties of Daxing.

05:35.768 --> 05:37.888
You won't see them when
you return to the grasslands.

05:38.304 --> 05:41.453
I had the people in the palace
prepare many things for you too as well.

05:41.493 --> 05:43.542
When the time comes,
you should take them all.

05:44.477 --> 05:45.477
Okay, okay, okay.

05:45.745 --> 05:46.745
I'll listen to you.

05:49.482 --> 05:50.482
Let's go.

06:03.836 --> 06:04.836
Tell me,

06:05.798 --> 06:07.800
if you weren't the prince of Talhan

06:08.000 --> 06:09.602
and I weren't a prince of Daxing,

06:10.570 --> 06:14.407
would we be as ordinary and happy as them?

06:17.844 --> 06:18.844
A Qi,

06:19.278 --> 06:20.680
No matter who you are

06:21.180 --> 06:22.348
or who you're with,

06:23.449 --> 06:24.650
you'll always be happy.

06:27.954 --> 06:29.355
It's because of you

06:29.555 --> 06:31.424
that I have a chance to start over.

06:32.558 --> 06:34.026
Without you,

06:35.595 --> 06:37.196
none of this would have happened.

06:38.865 --> 06:40.385
How could I even talk about happiness?

06:43.569 --> 06:44.837
So I'm that important.

06:46.372 --> 06:47.372
Let's go.

06:47.540 --> 06:48.820
Let's go take a look over there.

06:51.831 --> 06:52.265
Yanzhi,

06:52.478 --> 06:53.479
I've figured it out.

06:54.013 --> 06:55.648
When you come back from the grasslands,

06:55.915 --> 06:58.785
let's first travel all over the country.

06:59.452 --> 07:00.486
Then,

07:01.621 --> 07:02.889
and when we're old,

07:03.122 --> 07:04.590
let's settle down in Jiangnan.

07:04.690 --> 07:05.690
What do you think?

07:19.305 --> 07:20.106
Master,

07:20.173 --> 07:21.240
you're finally here.

07:22.141 --> 07:23.141
Fifth Prince,

07:25.331 --> 07:28.092
I've heard that the Red Dust Brew
at the Piaoxiang Pavilion is superb.

07:28.127 --> 07:30.325
I never had the mind to taste it
before when I came here.

07:30.349 --> 07:32.351
Today, I'm just here for leisure.

07:32.952 --> 07:33.985
My subordinates just received some

07:33.986 --> 07:34.954
secret letters from Talhan.

07:34.987 --> 07:36.222
They're about Su He.

07:36.289 --> 07:36.989
Master,

07:36.990 --> 07:38.200
come with me to the second floor first.

07:38.224 --> 07:39.601
I'll accompany the Fifth Prince later.

07:39.625 --> 07:40.359
Waiter,

07:40.360 --> 07:42.161
bring a pot of Red
Dust Brew for this guest.

07:42.428 --> 07:42.795
Let's go.

07:42.795 --> 07:43.795
Okay.

07:43.996 --> 07:44.430
Come on,

07:44.430 --> 07:44.931
sir,

07:44.931 --> 07:45.931
this way please.

07:55.708 --> 07:56.708
Master,

07:59.011 --> 08:00.011
Wenjie,

08:00.713 --> 08:01.713
help me.

08:01.981 --> 08:03.483
Okay, okay.

08:06.619 --> 08:07.619
Master,

08:08.387 --> 08:09.388
how are you now?

08:11.791 --> 08:12.791
It's okay.

08:13.292 --> 08:14.293
I can still hold on.

08:14.861 --> 08:16.261
You can hold on for a while,

08:16.262 --> 08:17.262
but...

08:24.670 --> 08:25.671
this military token,

08:26.005 --> 08:27.606
have the accompanying secret envoy

08:27.607 --> 08:29.008
take it back to my eldest brother.

08:29.809 --> 08:30.809
Right now,

08:31.143 --> 08:32.478
without the threat of Su He,

08:34.480 --> 08:35.514
I believe

08:37.617 --> 08:40.353
my eldest brother can
definitely govern Talhan very well.

08:43.556 --> 08:44.590
In this way,

08:46.292 --> 08:47.426
I'll be at ease.

08:47.860 --> 08:49.395
Please don't say such things, Master.

08:50.196 --> 08:51.264
I don't believe

08:51.597 --> 08:53.266
the poison in your body can't be cured.

08:53.833 --> 08:55.668
Why not tell the Fifth Prince about this?

08:55.801 --> 08:56.869
As a prince,

08:57.003 --> 08:58.604
he can find any famous doctor.

09:00.907 --> 09:02.341
If it can be cured,

09:03.042 --> 09:04.644
how could I just sit and wait for death?

09:08.147 --> 09:09.147
But

09:11.336 --> 09:12.336
in this life,

09:13.853 --> 09:17.023
I've been able to help
A Qi clear away obstacles

09:18.391 --> 09:22.194
and help my eldest brother
eliminate treacherous officials.

09:25.765 --> 09:27.567
I have no regrets.

09:30.236 --> 09:33.839
But you've sacrificed
yourself for everyone.

09:34.840 --> 09:36.275
I think it's not worth it.

09:37.710 --> 09:39.345
Because in my eyes,

09:40.913 --> 09:42.281
you are the most important.

09:45.351 --> 09:46.351
Wenjie,

09:47.486 --> 09:50.590
It's been an honor to

09:52.124 --> 09:53.559
work with you in this life.

09:55.247 --> 09:56.281
If you

09:57.697 --> 09:59.999
still remember the affection between us,

10:07.306 --> 10:08.674
I have a request.

10:09.542 --> 10:10.542
Master,

10:11.310 --> 10:12.511
just tell me.

10:13.245 --> 10:14.847
I'll do my utmost.

10:16.248 --> 10:17.450
If one day,

10:19.318 --> 10:20.786
A Qi encounters difficulties,

10:30.563 --> 10:31.964
you must help him.

10:34.634 --> 10:35.634
Okay.

10:36.168 --> 10:37.168
Okay.

10:52.351 --> 10:54.353
Aren't you about to return to Talhan?

10:54.620 --> 10:56.222
Why are you still so busy with things?

10:56.689 --> 10:57.490
By the way,

10:57.491 --> 10:59.692
this Red Dust Brew is really delicious.

10:59.792 --> 11:00.993
No wonder it's so famous.

11:08.100 --> 11:09.100
Waiter,

11:09.502 --> 11:10.502
bring a pot of warm wine.

11:10.803 --> 11:11.803
Okay.

11:18.711 --> 11:20.279
You always like to drink cold wine.

11:21.280 --> 11:25.151
You'll get a headache the next day
if you drink too much.

11:29.021 --> 11:30.021
In the future,

11:30.523 --> 11:31.957
when I'm not by your side,

11:33.959 --> 11:35.479
you should take good care of yourself.

11:37.163 --> 11:38.631
Take good care of your body.

11:40.399 --> 11:41.801
Don't drink cold wine anymore.

11:44.837 --> 11:47.173
Your tribesmen must not know this,

11:47.440 --> 11:50.042
that their Feng Sun Prince
who gallops across the grasslands

11:50.076 --> 11:51.877
has such a fussy side.

11:52.511 --> 11:53.279
Don't worry.

11:53.280 --> 11:55.081
I'll take good care of myself for you.

11:55.281 --> 11:56.614
I definitely won't give you a chance

11:56.615 --> 11:58.655
to dislike me for being
three years older than you.

12:03.923 --> 12:05.603
Why have you lost so much weight recently?

12:06.125 --> 12:06.926
Come on,

12:06.926 --> 12:07.926
eat more.

12:53.307 --> 12:56.174
(Yin Qi)

13:03.582 --> 13:05.151
I thought you were as hard as a rock,

13:05.451 --> 13:07.820
not showing any reluctance for so long.

13:08.354 --> 13:09.354
I didn't expect

13:12.224 --> 13:13.224
it was all an act.

13:20.232 --> 13:21.567
I've lived here for ten years,

13:22.034 --> 13:23.402
almost half of my life.

13:24.436 --> 13:25.638
How could I let go?

13:27.473 --> 13:28.807
How old are you?

13:29.508 --> 13:32.211
We still have the rest
of our lives together.

13:37.183 --> 13:38.183
Speaking of which,

13:39.652 --> 13:41.732
I haven't been to the
Yonghe Palace for a long time.

13:45.724 --> 13:47.364
The last time I came to the Yonghe Palace

13:48.327 --> 13:50.462
was after sending my
mother back to Jiangnan.

13:51.564 --> 13:52.765
During that time,

13:53.933 --> 13:55.968
I haven't dared to come
to my mother's residence,

13:56.969 --> 13:58.470
afraid that a single mistake

13:58.904 --> 14:00.639
would prevent me from changing our fates.

14:02.408 --> 14:03.876
I'd have no face to face my mother.

14:08.913 --> 14:11.153
Even if you didn't change the outcome
of your past life,

14:11.650 --> 14:13.252
Concubine Chen wouldn't blame you.

14:25.231 --> 14:26.232
There's something.

14:28.367 --> 14:30.169
I haven't told you and Heshu.

14:31.837 --> 14:35.040
Actually, before my mother left,

14:36.488 --> 14:37.728
it seemed like she sensed that

14:38.310 --> 14:40.045
I had come back from my past life.

14:42.848 --> 14:43.883
At that time,

14:46.719 --> 14:47.719
she even touched

14:48.020 --> 14:49.188
the place where I was shot

14:49.755 --> 14:50.889
and asked if it hurt.

14:55.261 --> 14:57.062
I only figured it out later.

14:57.863 --> 14:58.863
Perhaps

15:00.032 --> 15:02.868
my mother and I have a
deep mother-son bond.

15:08.340 --> 15:09.541
Concubine Chen

15:09.608 --> 15:11.243
was afraid that after she left,

15:11.610 --> 15:12.930
you would be bullied by Yin Zhou.

15:14.780 --> 15:15.780
By the way, A Qi,

15:16.248 --> 15:17.383
do you remember

15:17.583 --> 15:19.251
the last time we were here?

15:20.586 --> 15:21.586
A Qi,

15:22.087 --> 15:23.088
the last time you said

15:23.749 --> 15:25.749
to secretly send Concubine
Chen out of the palace.

15:26.171 --> 15:27.171
But why me?

15:27.326 --> 15:28.326
You're right.

15:28.594 --> 15:29.962
It was too risky.

15:30.930 --> 15:33.165
I shouldn't have risked
my mother's body either.

15:34.366 --> 15:35.768
At that time, the two of us

15:36.035 --> 15:37.569
had our own hidden agendas

15:37.836 --> 15:39.180
and wouldn't give in to each other.

15:39.204 --> 15:40.615
Neither knew what
the other was thinking

15:40.639 --> 15:41.839
or what they were going to do.

15:42.675 --> 15:44.543
If it weren't for my persistence,

15:45.611 --> 15:48.280
with your stubborn temperament of
not wanting to speak up,

15:48.681 --> 15:50.449
even if I lived ten more lives,

15:50.683 --> 15:52.685
I might not be able to change our fate.

16:08.767 --> 16:10.202
After I leave the capital,

16:15.074 --> 16:16.542
you must be very careful.

16:17.409 --> 16:18.811
Don't trust anyone,

16:19.478 --> 16:20.478
just like

16:22.414 --> 16:23.682
you were wary of me before.

16:25.724 --> 16:26.892
I've remembered it all.

16:28.287 --> 16:30.556
Why are you even more
worried about me than my mother?

16:53.912 --> 16:54.980
A Qi,

16:55.914 --> 16:56.954
Don't send me any further.

16:57.783 --> 16:58.783
If you send me further,

16:59.885 --> 17:01.653
you won't make it into the city before dark.

17:02.955 --> 17:03.955
But

17:04.089 --> 17:05.529
I want to see you off a bit further.

17:11.330 --> 17:12.431
If you keep sending me off,

17:12.931 --> 17:15.131
you'll end up sending me
all the way to the grasslands.

17:16.035 --> 17:16.802
Okay.

17:16.803 --> 17:18.003
I'll listen to you.

17:18.203 --> 17:19.605
But you have to promise me.

17:19.638 --> 17:20.472
Come back as soon as possible.

17:20.506 --> 17:21.607
The sooner, the better.

17:22.508 --> 17:23.508
And also,

17:23.742 --> 17:25.210
remember to write to me.

17:25.244 --> 17:27.346
I'll wait for your letters every day.

17:30.315 --> 17:31.315
I promise you.

20:28.147 --> 20:30.267
(Concubine Chen's Gravestone)

20:30.395 --> 20:31.395
Concubine Chen,

20:32.864 --> 20:33.864
I promised you.

20:34.232 --> 20:35.634
I've finally done it.

20:37.369 --> 20:38.369
Now,

20:43.942 --> 20:45.844
no one can stop A Qi

20:45.877 --> 20:47.412
from living the life he wants.

21:05.163 --> 21:06.565
But thinking carefully,

21:11.770 --> 21:15.007
I seem to have failed to
live up to your instructions.

21:17.075 --> 21:18.075
I promised

21:19.478 --> 21:21.013
to protect A Qi for a lifetime.

21:25.150 --> 21:28.787
Now I might have to break that promise.

21:34.593 --> 21:35.994
When I see you again,

21:37.329 --> 21:38.730
I'll apologize to you in person.

22:18.970 --> 22:19.970
Yanzhi,

22:20.372 --> 22:21.372
Yanzhi,

22:21.440 --> 22:22.607
why are you here?

22:24.456 --> 22:25.456
Yanzhi,

22:25.711 --> 22:26.711
wake up!

22:40.959 --> 22:41.959
Come here.

22:42.127 --> 22:43.127
Aunt Lin,

22:50.035 --> 22:51.103
This is Yanbo Tower.

22:53.405 --> 22:54.439
Why am I here?

22:55.207 --> 22:56.475
I was going to ask you that.

22:57.008 --> 22:59.044
Didn't you go back to
the capital with Qi'er?

22:59.845 --> 23:02.085
How did you end up fainting
in front of Tang'er's grave?

23:07.385 --> 23:09.888
This palace is truly no place for humans.

23:10.622 --> 23:12.391
Yin Zhou is so vicious.

23:13.759 --> 23:15.160
So according to you,

23:15.861 --> 23:17.996
Qi'er knows nothing about your poisoning.

23:20.198 --> 23:21.333
A Qi has

23:22.901 --> 23:24.436
a long road ahead of him.

23:25.403 --> 23:26.772
If he finds out,

23:27.606 --> 23:29.408
it'll be a heavy blow to him.

23:31.843 --> 23:32.344
One day,

23:32.345 --> 23:33.812
he'll get used to living without me.

23:35.347 --> 23:37.549
Qi'er is a sentimental child.

23:38.583 --> 23:40.185
He said he'd wait for you.

23:40.919 --> 23:41.919
What if

23:42.020 --> 23:43.789
he really waits for you his whole life?

23:44.523 --> 23:45.690
If he's willing to wait,

23:47.993 --> 23:49.793
at least he has something
to look forward to.

23:51.530 --> 23:53.131
If he knows the whole truth,

23:54.199 --> 23:55.400
it'll only make him suffer.

23:57.569 --> 24:00.405
My name, Lin Jianshuang,
isn't for nothing.

24:00.872 --> 24:01.872
You can rest assured.

24:02.274 --> 24:04.209
Even if I have to search the whole country,

24:04.409 --> 24:06.444
I'll definitely cure the
poison in your body.

24:07.946 --> 24:10.449
Just stay at Yanbo Tower peacefully.

24:10.749 --> 24:11.749
Aunt Lin,

24:12.451 --> 24:13.451
In this life,

24:14.386 --> 24:15.386
being able to accompany A Qi

24:15.387 --> 24:17.227
through the most
important journey of his life

24:17.622 --> 24:18.790
is enough for me.

24:24.062 --> 24:24.563
By the way,

24:24.563 --> 24:25.363
Aunt Lin,

24:25.530 --> 24:28.366
could you please get me
some writing materials?

24:28.567 --> 24:30.769
I promised to write to A Qi.

24:32.170 --> 24:33.170
Okay.

24:42.147 --> 24:43.147
Aunt Lin,

24:43.448 --> 24:45.383
please give this letter to A Qi for me.

24:46.318 --> 24:48.053
He'll be at ease after receiving it.

24:48.420 --> 24:49.420
Okay.

24:50.021 --> 24:51.021
Brother Yanzhi,

24:51.523 --> 24:52.324
You've finished

24:52.325 --> 24:53.885
dealing with palace affairs so quickly.

24:53.925 --> 24:55.965
Why didn't you tell me you
were coming to Jiangnan?

24:56.455 --> 24:57.455
Where's my royal brother?

24:57.796 --> 24:58.597
Where is he?

24:58.797 --> 24:59.797
It's just me.

24:59.931 --> 25:00.799
A Qi didn't come.

25:00.799 --> 25:01.799
I want to

25:02.467 --> 25:03.435
go back to Talhan.

25:03.468 --> 25:04.468
I'm just passing by here.

25:05.103 --> 25:06.605
Don't tell your royal brother.

25:08.740 --> 25:09.740
I

25:10.642 --> 25:11.642
I'm

25:11.743 --> 25:12.878
suffering from a cold.

25:13.111 --> 25:14.212
I'm afraid it'll worry him.

25:26.291 --> 25:27.291
Wen Jie,

25:27.425 --> 25:29.194
I received a letter from Yanzhi.

25:30.362 --> 25:31.963
Master sent a letter so quickly.

25:32.664 --> 25:34.966
He must be close to Talhan by now.

25:35.967 --> 25:37.044
He was in a hurry on the way,

25:37.068 --> 25:37.802
so he only had time

25:37.803 --> 25:39.547
to send this letter to
let us know he's safe.

25:39.571 --> 25:40.681
He's afraid you'll worry about him.

25:40.705 --> 25:41.705
He asked me to tell you

25:41.706 --> 25:42.741
that he's doing fine.

25:43.141 --> 25:44.141
Okay.

25:44.743 --> 25:45.743
As long as he's safe.

25:48.246 --> 25:49.581
You seem strange.

25:50.225 --> 25:52.894
Yanzhi will come back to Daxing
after finishing things this time.

25:52.918 --> 25:53.919
It won't be long.

25:54.719 --> 25:56.788
What if Master

25:57.355 --> 25:58.590
takes many years this time?

26:01.960 --> 26:02.960
With Yanzhi's abilities,

26:02.961 --> 26:03.971
he'll definitely come
back within three years.

26:03.995 --> 26:05.196
He will definitely come back.

26:05.597 --> 26:06.398
What's wrong?

26:06.531 --> 26:08.033
Don't you trust your lord?

26:31.589 --> 26:32.600
What are you thinking about?

26:32.624 --> 26:33.792
You're absent-minded.

26:37.529 --> 26:38.530
I'm wondering

26:39.264 --> 26:41.966
why Brother Yanzhi always tells me

26:41.967 --> 26:43.067
not to tell my royal brother

26:43.068 --> 26:44.436
about him being at Yanbo Tower.

26:45.370 --> 26:46.871
If he just wants to rest,

26:47.172 --> 26:47.839
then why

26:47.840 --> 26:49.007
can't my royal brother know?

26:50.909 --> 26:52.042
You also think Brother Yanzhi's

26:52.043 --> 26:53.603
visit to Jiangnan this time is strange.

26:54.713 --> 26:56.680
The other day, I saw
my aunt bring a stranger

26:56.681 --> 26:58.583
into Brother Yanzhi's room.

26:58.750 --> 27:00.790
But when I asked my aunt
who that person was later,

27:01.052 --> 27:02.587
she wouldn't tell me anything.

27:08.727 --> 27:09.727
It seems like

27:09.794 --> 27:11.262
we need to think of a way.

27:15.667 --> 27:16.667
Yes.

27:16.901 --> 27:18.003
Hold the hilt like this,

27:23.508 --> 27:24.508
thrust it out.

27:27.245 --> 27:29.648
Good job, good job!

27:30.515 --> 27:32.117
Zhou'er is going to ascend the throne.

27:32.484 --> 27:33.985
I'm going to be the Empress Dowager.

27:34.486 --> 27:36.287
Zhou'er is going to ascend the throne.

27:36.755 --> 27:38.356
Concubine Chen is also dead.

27:38.577 --> 27:41.312
I killed Concubine Chen.

27:42.394 --> 27:43.954
What do you mean by what you just said?

27:44.562 --> 27:47.065
Did you kill my mother?

27:48.306 --> 27:49.574
During the hunt,

27:50.194 --> 27:52.396
she insisted on drinking your wine.

27:53.271 --> 27:54.639
Since she wanted to die,

27:55.113 --> 27:56.714
I let her die.

27:58.810 --> 28:00.612
Explain it clearly to me.

28:01.299 --> 28:04.502
What exactly happened
at the hunting ground?

28:11.389 --> 28:12.424
Strange.

28:12.557 --> 28:13.558
It's really strange.

28:14.959 --> 28:15.959
How?

28:17.796 --> 28:19.230
According to my diagnosis,

28:19.564 --> 28:21.764
the young master should
have contracted a cold illness.

28:22.033 --> 28:23.468
If we're talking about poisoning,

28:23.768 --> 28:25.370
then there's only one possibility.

28:25.804 --> 28:27.872
This poison can penetrate
the internal organs,

28:28.245 --> 28:29.580
causing a cold illness

28:29.874 --> 28:31.009
and death from coughing.

28:33.244 --> 28:34.244
Cold illness.

28:35.453 --> 28:36.453
Coughing.

28:40.452 --> 28:41.453
Concubine Chen,

28:45.990 --> 28:47.191
My mother was poisoned.

28:49.728 --> 28:51.029
I remember now.

28:51.563 --> 28:52.964
Your young master

28:53.331 --> 28:54.766
won't survive either.

28:54.846 --> 28:56.381
What have you done to Yanzhi again?

28:56.901 --> 28:58.045
Your Royal Highness, the Fifth Prince,

28:58.069 --> 28:59.346
ever since the Crown Prince passed away,

28:59.370 --> 29:00.839
the Empress has been acting crazy.

29:00.863 --> 29:02.457
You can't take her words seriously.

29:02.481 --> 29:03.743
He won't survive either.

29:07.746 --> 29:08.746
I didn't expect

29:11.082 --> 29:12.516
that Tang'er and you

29:12.517 --> 29:13.917
were poisoned with the same poison.

29:15.053 --> 29:16.053
Doctor,

29:16.087 --> 29:17.555
is there a way to cure it?

29:18.723 --> 29:21.092
I've never seen this poison before.

29:21.359 --> 29:24.062
I can only prescribe some medicine
to relieve the coughing pain.

29:24.662 --> 29:25.797
As for curing it,

29:26.164 --> 29:27.832
I really can't do it.

29:29.501 --> 29:30.501
Doctor,

29:32.303 --> 29:33.638
how long do I have left?

29:34.171 --> 29:35.740
The young master is physically strong.

29:36.074 --> 29:38.042
With medicine to delay the onset,

29:38.209 --> 29:40.011
he might live for three months.

29:48.119 --> 29:49.519
I'm going to tell my royal brother.

30:03.334 --> 30:04.334
What's wrong with Yanzhi?

30:04.536 --> 30:05.470
What exactly is wrong with Yanzhi?

30:05.471 --> 30:06.471
Tell me quickly.

30:06.971 --> 30:07.971
You,

30:08.239 --> 30:09.240
you already know...?

30:09.874 --> 30:11.209
What do you mean he's dying?

30:11.709 --> 30:13.478
Tell me everything you know quickly.

30:13.658 --> 30:14.663
When Master was in Jiangnan,

30:14.687 --> 30:16.087
Yin Zhou poisoned him.

30:17.282 --> 30:18.362
He was afraid you'd be sad,

30:18.550 --> 30:19.910
so he told us not to say anything.

30:20.318 --> 30:21.553
How did you find out?

30:22.287 --> 30:23.727
He didn't go back to the grasslands.

30:24.389 --> 30:25.389
Where is he?

30:25.957 --> 30:27.158
I don't know.

30:27.625 --> 30:28.903
Your Royal Highness, the Fifth Prince,

30:28.927 --> 30:30.962
I advise you not to
look for Master anymore.

30:31.629 --> 30:32.997
He doesn't want you to know,

30:33.031 --> 30:35.366
precisely because he doesn't
want you to to watch him die.

30:35.987 --> 30:37.307
He's been struggling for his life

30:37.635 --> 30:39.636
just so you can live peacefully.

30:39.637 --> 30:40.371
Why can't you just

30:40.371 --> 30:41.371
fulfill his wish?

30:42.206 --> 30:43.306
If he dies,

30:43.330 --> 30:44.398
how can I live peacefully?

30:46.411 --> 30:47.478
Anyway, I don't know.

30:47.745 --> 30:49.080
It's useless to press me.

30:49.581 --> 30:51.049
I'll definitely find out.

31:01.739 --> 31:02.373
Your Royal Highness,

31:02.560 --> 31:03.394
where is Yanzhi?

31:03.461 --> 31:04.462
Any news?

31:05.997 --> 31:08.442
The young master seems to
have deliberately hidden his whereabouts.

31:08.466 --> 31:10.786
No post stations along the way
have seen the young master.

31:12.503 --> 31:13.104
Your Royal Highness,

31:13.204 --> 31:15.084
I've received a letter
from the Sixth Princess.

31:21.446 --> 31:23.447
Should I go and persuade
Your Royal Highness?

31:23.448 --> 31:24.916
I think it's better not.

31:25.617 --> 31:26.451
Royal brother,

31:26.452 --> 31:27.751
Pei Yanzhi has been poisoned deeply.

31:27.752 --> 31:28.620
He doesn't have long to live.

31:28.621 --> 31:30.581
I hope the Fifth Royal
Brother will come quickly.

31:30.755 --> 31:31.755
Yanzhi,

31:32.023 --> 31:33.024
Yanzhi is in Jiangnan.

31:34.893 --> 31:35.693
Duan Yong,

31:35.793 --> 31:37.061
hurry and tell Doctor Bai

31:37.161 --> 31:38.563
to come with me to Jiangnan.

31:39.330 --> 31:40.330
Go to Jiangnan again?

31:40.565 --> 31:42.634
Isn't the young master in the grasslands?

31:42.667 --> 31:43.677
Don't ask so many questions.

31:43.701 --> 31:44.469
Hurry and go.

31:44.469 --> 31:45.469
Don't delay.

31:46.204 --> 31:46.638
Yes.

31:46.671 --> 31:47.671
Yes.

31:51.442 --> 31:52.477
What did you say?

31:52.877 --> 31:54.245
You're going to Jiangnan.

31:55.647 --> 31:57.048
Just for that hostage.

31:59.717 --> 32:02.287
Yanzhi is the only
person I cherish in my life.

32:02.420 --> 32:04.298
The one I want to spend
the rest of my life with.

32:04.322 --> 32:06.333
We've already pledged our
eternal love to each other.

32:06.357 --> 32:07.997
Promising to never part in this lifetime.

32:08.559 --> 32:11.963
So I must go to Jiangnan to save him.

32:12.423 --> 32:13.423
How dare you!

32:15.700 --> 32:16.501
Qi'er.

32:16.701 --> 32:18.703
You've disappointed me greatly.

32:19.170 --> 32:21.673
You know very well that
after your eldest royal brother left.

32:21.873 --> 32:24.409
You're the only prince I can rely on.

32:24.642 --> 32:26.611
Yet you're so stubborn and unenlightened.

32:27.512 --> 32:29.580
You've not only disappointed me.

32:30.234 --> 32:32.984
But also the entire Daxing Kingdom.

32:38.582 --> 32:39.582
Father.

32:40.091 --> 32:42.359
Please forgive my words today, for speaking out of turn.

32:43.027 --> 32:45.063
But I want to tell you, Father.

32:45.709 --> 32:47.269
You're still in the prime of your life,

32:47.612 --> 32:49.766
with plenty of time to groom the Seventh Prince.

32:50.234 --> 32:52.804
The future ten or twenty years of Daxing

32:52.828 --> 32:54.188
will always belong to you, Father.

32:55.506 --> 32:56.841
As for me.

32:58.109 --> 33:00.311
You can demote me to a commoner

33:00.345 --> 33:01.546
I have no complaints.

33:02.847 --> 33:03.847
Rebellious son.

33:03.948 --> 33:04.948
Rebellious son.

33:05.350 --> 33:08.686
Do you really think Daxing can't
survive without a prince like you?

33:08.953 --> 33:10.521
Come back to me!

33:10.788 --> 33:11.788
Come back!

33:39.984 --> 33:40.785
Yanzhi.

33:40.985 --> 33:41.985
You're awake.

33:43.020 --> 33:44.020
A Qi.

33:44.355 --> 33:45.355
What are you...

33:51.396 --> 33:52.430
Where am I?

33:52.797 --> 33:54.031
I asked Doctor Bai.

33:54.599 --> 33:57.602
He said the hot springs at the
imperial palace are good for your health.

33:58.069 --> 33:59.984
So I brought you from Yanbo Tower back here.

34:03.708 --> 34:05.009
You know now.

34:08.713 --> 34:09.713
So.

34:10.548 --> 34:17.955
Before you left the capital, The
words you said to me were all farewells.

34:29.067 --> 34:30.067
A Qi.

34:34.405 --> 34:35.740
You shouldn't have come here.

34:36.207 --> 34:37.742
Now is not the time for this.

34:38.242 --> 34:39.043
Yanzhi.

34:39.083 --> 34:40.184
Trust me.

34:40.244 --> 34:42.013
I'll definitely find a way to cure you.

34:44.148 --> 34:45.148
A Qi.

34:45.483 --> 34:46.483
A Qi.

34:46.884 --> 34:47.884
A Qi.

34:56.394 --> 34:57.394
You're crazy.

34:58.629 --> 35:00.031
This is your plan?

35:00.431 --> 35:01.431
To die?

35:02.366 --> 35:05.629
Only if I die will the gods
give me another chance.

35:05.803 --> 35:07.772
What if the gods don't
give you another chance?

35:10.675 --> 35:12.043
Then you'll drown.

35:21.071 --> 35:23.497
Have you forgotten all the
hardships we've faced on our journey?

35:23.521 --> 35:24.521
If you...

35:27.024 --> 35:28.392
if you really die,

35:30.194 --> 35:31.863
will you be able to face Concubine Chen?

35:31.886 --> 35:33.721
Can't I just give up on my own life?

35:39.670 --> 35:40.670
Yanzhi.

35:43.007 --> 35:44.007
What should I do?

35:52.316 --> 35:56.220
Don't place your hopes on such things.

36:01.792 --> 36:02.792
A Qi.

36:03.528 --> 36:04.562
Come back with me.

36:05.396 --> 36:06.998
Or you'll catch a cold.

36:13.004 --> 36:14.972
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

36:15.806 --> 36:17.542
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

36:20.278 --> 36:21.278
Why?

36:23.381 --> 36:25.149
I don't want you to leave me.

36:25.783 --> 36:26.783
I don't want it.

36:41.666 --> 36:43.067
Have some hot water.

36:43.434 --> 36:44.802
You've been outside for so long.

36:45.202 --> 36:46.202
Don't catch a cold.

37:12.730 --> 37:14.165
How could you be so foolish?

37:18.703 --> 37:20.304
Do you really believe

37:22.006 --> 37:23.806
the eternal gods will
give us another chance?

37:24.675 --> 37:26.010
Of course I believe.

37:31.749 --> 37:33.651
I won't give up easily.

37:36.087 --> 37:38.289
I'll definitely find a way to save you.

37:44.629 --> 37:46.364
Our A Qi has really grown up.

37:49.567 --> 37:50.567
Masterminding strategies.

37:50.968 --> 37:51.969
Never giving up.

37:57.074 --> 37:58.943
Increasingly resembling a crown prince.

38:01.145 --> 38:03.247
You never consider my feelings.

38:03.948 --> 38:11.282
Do you think that after you leave I
can just pretend that nothing happened?

38:11.789 --> 38:13.991
And I can continue
being the Fifth Prince?

38:24.802 --> 38:25.802
I'm sorry.

38:30.274 --> 38:31.676
I couldn't think of a better way.

38:38.349 --> 38:40.351
I didn't want you to see me like this now.

38:45.890 --> 38:46.890
I want...

38:48.926 --> 38:49.926
my A Qi...

38:54.932 --> 38:56.100
to be happy.

39:16.587 --> 39:17.587
Your Highness

39:18.389 --> 39:20.767
I've been browsing through
ancient texts these past few days.

39:20.791 --> 39:24.161
And discovered that there is indeed a
strange poison in Japan called Amantuo.

39:24.795 --> 39:27.998
This poison is strange in that
it doesn't kill immediately,

39:28.232 --> 39:29.600
but slowly takes effect,

39:29.834 --> 39:31.674
rventually causing death
by coughing up blood.

39:32.770 --> 39:37.541
The whole process looks like contracting a
severe cold and dying from an incurable illness.

39:39.009 --> 39:43.080
The symptoms of Concubine
Chen and the young master all match up.

39:50.087 --> 39:51.087
Nan Xing.

39:51.689 --> 39:52.689
You...

39:53.324 --> 39:54.324
do you have a way?

39:58.396 --> 39:59.396
A Qi.

40:00.097 --> 40:01.499
Since I came to Jiangnan.

40:02.333 --> 40:04.668
Aunt Lin has found many famous doctors to treat me.

40:06.036 --> 40:09.632
Each doctor has said that they don't
know how to detoxify this poison.

40:11.609 --> 40:12.609
A Qi.

40:17.982 --> 40:20.731
I indeed have no way to detoxify it.

40:21.252 --> 40:22.612
I can only follow the prescription

40:22.787 --> 40:24.227
to regulate the young master's body,

40:24.688 --> 40:27.823
and see if it can suppress the cold
symptoms in the young master's body.

40:28.826 --> 40:30.795
As for completely detoxifying it...

40:31.962 --> 40:32.962
I'm afraid...

40:36.066 --> 40:37.368
I know what you mean.

40:40.004 --> 40:42.505
You're afraid that in the end
I'll end up with nothing.

40:43.407 --> 40:44.608
But at this point,

40:45.476 --> 40:48.045
there's nothing I can't accept.

40:52.983 --> 40:54.051
Don't worry.

40:54.852 --> 40:56.387
This time I won't run away.

40:56.821 --> 40:58.301
As long as there's a glimmer of hope,

40:59.123 --> 41:00.524
I won't give up.

42:06.891 --> 42:08.492
Is it a letter from the palace?

42:10.261 --> 42:11.262
It says.

42:11.996 --> 42:13.063
Father is seriously ill

42:13.864 --> 42:15.442
and wants me to return
to the capital immediately

42:15.466 --> 42:17.234
to handle government affairs.

42:18.068 --> 42:19.036
But when I left the capital.

42:19.037 --> 42:20.437
Father was clearly fine.

42:22.673 --> 42:24.141
I can't go back now.

42:24.241 --> 42:25.241
A Qi.

42:26.644 --> 42:27.644
Now.

42:27.878 --> 42:29.656
The heavy responsibility
of reorganizing the court

42:29.680 --> 42:30.848
has fallen on to you.

42:32.149 --> 42:33.550
You must go back.

42:35.352 --> 42:36.353
But you...

42:38.155 --> 42:39.155
I...

42:40.291 --> 42:43.394
My body is getting thinner every day.

42:44.228 --> 42:45.563
You've been by my side all along.

42:46.356 --> 42:48.592
Looking into your eyes...

42:49.700 --> 42:52.469
going from hopeful to
increasingly desperate...

42:53.404 --> 42:54.872
is more painful than killing me.

42:57.841 --> 42:58.841
A Qi.

43:00.444 --> 43:01.645
Go back to the palace.

43:02.880 --> 43:04.481
Don't continue to stay with me.

43:12.156 --> 43:13.156
Brother.

43:13.223 --> 43:14.425
How is father's illness?

43:18.662 --> 43:19.663
Father is seriously ill.

43:19.763 --> 43:21.241
And there's no one to oversee the country.

43:21.265 --> 43:21.832
Brother.

43:21.833 --> 43:23.233
We must set off as soon as possible

43:24.902 --> 43:26.003
and return to the capital.

43:27.237 --> 43:28.639
Yanzhi's illness hasn't healed yet.

43:29.073 --> 43:30.139
I can't go back.

43:30.140 --> 43:31.140
A Qi.

43:36.080 --> 43:38.849
How can matters of the country
and the people be taken lightly?

43:39.116 --> 43:40.484
Under the heavens,

43:41.051 --> 43:42.987
countless people are counting on you.

43:45.356 --> 43:46.223
How could I possibly

43:46.290 --> 43:48.250
leave you behind and
return to the capital alone?

43:48.626 --> 43:51.061
Or come back to the capital with me.

43:51.595 --> 43:52.062
Then

43:52.129 --> 43:54.131
I'll find the best doctors to cure you.

43:55.399 --> 43:56.399
Qi'er.

43:56.834 --> 43:57.834
Yanzhi

43:58.035 --> 44:00.604
I was just looking for
you to discuss this matter.

44:01.405 --> 44:04.608
If Yanzhi continues to be
treated in the Central Plains.

44:06.076 --> 44:09.880
I'm afraid he'll end up like Tang'er.

44:12.349 --> 44:13.550
At this point.

44:14.051 --> 44:16.887
We can only take Yanzhi
to Japan and give it a try.

44:21.558 --> 44:22.558
Japan.

44:23.961 --> 44:26.363
I previously sent a letter to Japan

44:26.816 --> 44:28.418
asking my business partners.

44:28.632 --> 44:30.167
I was waiting for a reply.

44:30.567 --> 44:33.070
But now, after thinking it over.

44:33.270 --> 44:35.882
It's better to take advantage of
Yanzhi's still relatively good health.

44:35.906 --> 44:39.043
And let me take him to Japan for treatment.

44:39.843 --> 44:41.745
Perhaps there's still a chance.

44:46.517 --> 44:47.517
Japan.

44:48.686 --> 44:50.487
Amandtuo is a strange poison from Japan.

44:51.221 --> 44:53.791
Perhaps there's a way to detoxify it there.

44:55.793 --> 44:56.593
Yanzhi.

44:56.594 --> 44:57.795
Let's pack our things now.

44:57.828 --> 44:58.828
And hurry to Japan.

45:04.301 --> 45:05.301
A Qi.

45:06.036 --> 45:07.036
You can't go.

45:08.405 --> 45:10.207
You have more important things to do.

45:14.011 --> 45:15.011
Your Highness.

45:15.412 --> 45:17.412
The government affairs
of Daxing can't be delayed.

45:18.014 --> 45:19.950
I know you care deeply
about the young master.

45:20.744 --> 45:23.680
I will go to Japan with the young master

45:24.955 --> 45:27.591
I'll take care of the young
master along the way.

45:27.825 --> 45:29.026
You can rest assured.

45:33.030 --> 45:34.030
Nan Xing.

45:36.200 --> 45:37.835
With Aunt Lin and Doctor Bai,

45:38.502 --> 45:41.839
Accompanying Brother Yanzhi to Japan,
brother, you can rest assured now.

45:43.073 --> 45:43.674
Yes.

45:43.674 --> 45:44.274
Fifth Prince.

45:44.308 --> 45:45.609
You have to trust my aunt.

45:45.802 --> 45:47.206
When she promises something to someone.

45:47.230 --> 45:48.550
She'll definitely make it happen.

46:14.505 --> 46:15.806
What are you thinking about?

46:20.544 --> 46:21.645
I'm thinking about.

46:23.747 --> 46:25.125
The last Mid-Autumn Festival night.

46:25.149 --> 46:26.949
We were supposed to
make wishes by the river.

46:27.684 --> 46:30.287
Unfortunately, it didn't happen.

46:31.522 --> 46:32.762
Later, we made wishes together.

46:33.557 --> 46:34.691
The moon that night

46:35.893 --> 46:38.053
was not as round as it was
on the Mid-Autumn Festival.

46:38.729 --> 46:39.729
Perhaps

46:40.430 --> 46:42.032
the wishes made may not be as effective.

46:42.859 --> 46:43.859
So what?

46:44.835 --> 46:45.969
In the future,

46:46.703 --> 46:48.605
we can set off sky lanterns every day

46:49.206 --> 46:50.326
and make wishes to the moon,

46:51.008 --> 46:52.242
annoying the gods to death

46:52.676 --> 46:54.901
so that they have no choice but to
fulfill our wishes.

47:01.785 --> 47:02.785
A Qi,

47:02.986 --> 47:04.121
why don't we

47:04.922 --> 47:05.922
be together today

47:05.956 --> 47:07.224
and make wishes to the gods

47:07.324 --> 47:08.444
to make up for past regrets?

47:13.230 --> 47:15.766
The believer Yin Qi
makes a wish to the gods,

47:16.833 --> 47:19.269
hoping that the gods will bless my Yanzhi

47:20.204 --> 47:21.204
on his journey to Japan,

47:21.271 --> 47:22.272
to return cured

47:23.240 --> 47:26.410
and stay by my side forever,

47:27.444 --> 47:29.044
spending the rest of our lives together.

47:37.087 --> 47:38.087
God,

47:39.590 --> 47:40.691
please bless

47:40.724 --> 47:42.226
my A Qi

47:43.827 --> 47:45.362
to live safely.

47:59.509 --> 48:01.510
The true god in heaven,

48:01.511 --> 48:04.747
A Qi and I love each other deeply,

48:04.748 --> 48:06.850
yet we cannot grow old together.

48:08.752 --> 48:11.354
If you truly have power,

48:11.355 --> 48:12.521
please bless the man I
love deeply before me

48:12.522 --> 48:14.458
that he may no longer suffer

48:15.959 --> 48:19.062
and live in peace and
prosperity in the future.

48:19.122 --> 48:21.224
May he be safe and well.

49:45.511 --> 49:48.098
(Three years later)

50:02.766 --> 50:04.001
I say, Miss,

50:04.234 --> 50:08.171
It's fine that you gave gave that wine ordered
by Mr. Zhang to Mr. Li to drink yesterday,

50:08.271 --> 50:09.438
but after the wine was finished,

50:09.439 --> 50:11.250
you didn't even go to the wine shop
to buy more to replenish it.

50:11.274 --> 50:12.285
If you continue to do business like this,

50:12.308 --> 50:14.508
my Yanbo Tower will close
down sooner rather than later.

50:15.012 --> 50:16.213
I know I was wrong.

50:16.313 --> 50:17.480
I'll have Duan Yi and Duan Yong

50:17.481 --> 50:19.349
go buy the wine and make it up to you.

50:24.154 --> 50:24.955
Does my Lin family lack

50:24.956 --> 50:26.590
a few jars of wine like this?

50:26.623 --> 50:27.824
This isn't about the wine.

50:29.092 --> 50:30.394
It's not about the wine.

50:30.961 --> 50:31.961
What is it then?

50:32.662 --> 50:33.030
Your Highness.

50:33.030 --> 50:33.797
Your Highness.

50:33.797 --> 50:34.264
Elder brother.

50:34.331 --> 50:35.332
What brings you here?

50:37.234 --> 50:38.001
What's the matter?

50:38.001 --> 50:38.969
I came to see you.

50:38.993 --> 50:39.993
Aren't I welcome?

50:40.303 --> 50:41.004
Welcome, welcome.

50:41.004 --> 50:42.004
Of course I welcome you.

50:42.406 --> 50:44.017
How long do you plan to
stay in Jiangnan this time?

50:44.041 --> 50:45.742
I'll prepare a guest room right away.

50:45.909 --> 50:46.510
No hurry.

50:46.510 --> 50:47.077
Heshu,

50:47.077 --> 50:47.711
this time,

50:48.078 --> 50:49.598
I don't plan to return to the capital.

50:51.481 --> 50:52.481
Really, elder brother?

50:52.649 --> 50:53.884
You're not lying to me, right?

50:54.151 --> 50:54.351
You...

50:54.751 --> 50:56.253
How did you persuade Father Emperor?

50:57.320 --> 50:59.289
Seventh brother has
improved a lot this year.

51:00.309 --> 51:02.145
He's now fully-fledged

51:02.378 --> 51:03.946
and can handle things on his own.

51:04.761 --> 51:06.430
Since I've completed my mission,

51:06.830 --> 51:08.832
Father Emperor naturally couldn't stop me.

51:10.233 --> 51:11.568
That's wonderful.

51:11.701 --> 51:12.701
Xianyue,

51:13.003 --> 51:15.238
Tonight, I'll throw a grand banquet

51:15.272 --> 51:17.752
and invite my brother to taste
all the delicacies of Jiangnan.

51:17.808 --> 51:18.608
No problem.

51:18.632 --> 51:19.900
Just put it on your tab.

51:23.447 --> 51:24.948
Seeing you doing so well,

51:25.248 --> 51:26.650
I can rest assured.

51:30.554 --> 51:33.957
After that, I want to
go to Talhan again.

51:36.827 --> 51:37.827
Brother...

51:38.028 --> 51:38.795
You...

51:38.795 --> 51:39.795
Actually, I...

51:43.333 --> 51:44.333
I know.

51:44.968 --> 51:47.771
Aunt Lin was afraid I
would fall into despair

51:47.804 --> 51:48.804
and never recover.

51:49.106 --> 51:52.008
So she did everything she
could to take Yanzhi away.

51:54.344 --> 51:55.479
In these three years,

51:56.112 --> 51:57.581
I've been thinking every day

51:57.948 --> 51:59.508
about the moments I shared with Yanzhi,

52:00.650 --> 52:01.650
remembering him

52:03.253 --> 52:04.554
and every word he said to me,

52:04.788 --> 52:06.389
saying he would always be by my side.

52:08.492 --> 52:10.012
Actually, he didn't break his promise.

52:10.527 --> 52:11.828
In my heart,

52:12.562 --> 52:14.030
he has always been with me.

52:17.167 --> 52:19.035
This time, when I go to Talhan,

52:20.403 --> 52:22.243
afterwards I'll go to Japan to find him again.

52:25.542 --> 52:26.610
Sister Aruna

52:26.810 --> 52:28.210
wrote to say she's getting married.

52:28.478 --> 52:28.845
Brother,

52:28.846 --> 52:31.248
you can go in Yanzhi's
place to see her off.

52:51.261 --> 52:52.261
Yanzhi...

52:53.036 --> 52:54.747
I can't believe that
in the blink of an eye,

52:54.771 --> 52:56.173
three years have passed so quickly.

52:57.340 --> 52:58.241
The events of my past life

52:58.242 --> 52:59.643
are almost fading from my memory.

53:00.990 --> 53:02.858
Since the gods have given us this chance

53:03.013 --> 53:04.213
to meet again,

53:04.214 --> 53:06.082
why do they have to keep us apart?

53:07.250 --> 53:08.250
Yanzhi...

53:08.852 --> 53:10.220
Whether you're alive or dead,

53:10.720 --> 53:12.588
even if you're in the underworld,

53:12.589 --> 53:14.724
I'll find you.

53:15.084 --> 53:17.186
Even if the gods try to stop us,

53:17.594 --> 53:19.529
as long as I don't give up,

53:20.397 --> 53:22.265
what can they do to me?

54:32.502 --> 54:33.637
Yanzhi...

54:35.405 --> 54:36.640
You're mine.

54:43.246 --> 54:44.848
When will you finally admit

54:46.750 --> 54:47.751
your feelings for me?

55:23.779 --> 55:33.266
(The End)
